text: Key Markets is the eighth studio album by British electronic music duo Sleaford Mods. It was released on 24 July 2015 through Harbinger Sound. ==Reception== At Metacritic, which assigns a normalized rating out of 100 to reviews from mainstream critics, Key Markets received an average score of 81 based on twenty reviews, indicating "universal acclaim". It was one of the 19 records nominated for the IMPALA Album of the Year Award 2015. ===Accolades=== {|class="sortable wikitable" |- ! Publication ! Accolade ! Year !
